{"ja183:0.1":"Jataka ","ja183:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja183:0.3":"Asadisavagga ","ja183:0.4":"3. Valodakajataka ","ja183:1.1":"“Valodakam apparasam nihinam, ","ja183:1.2":"Pitva mado jayati gadrabhanam; ","ja183:1.3":"Imanca pitvana rasam panitam, ","ja183:1.4":"Mado na sanjayati sindhavanam”. ","ja183:2.1":"“Appam pivitvana nihinajacco, ","ja183:2.2":"So majjati tena janinda puttho; ","ja183:2.3":"Dhorayhasili ca kulamhi jato, ","ja183:2.4":"Na majjati aggarasam pivitva”ti. ","ja183:3.1":"Valodakajatakam tatiyam. "}